pebble-core 2.0.0 API

Packages 
Package Description
org.pebble.core
Provides Pebble's core algorithm implementation.
org.pebble.core.decoding
Provides Pebble's core decompression implementations.
org.pebble.core.decoding.iterators.ints
Provides Pebble's core list decompression iterators specific for lists containing elements of int type.
org.pebble.core.decoding.iterators.longs
Provides Pebble's core list decompression iterators specific for lists containing elements of long type.
org.pebble.core.encoding
Provides Pebble's core compression implementations.
org.pebble.core.encoding.commons
Provides Pebble's core compression common logic to int and long types.
org.pebble.core.encoding.ints
Provides Pebble's core compression implementation specific for lists containing elements of int type.
org.pebble.core.encoding.ints.datastructures
Provides Pebble's core compression utility data structures specific for lists containing elements of int type.
org.pebble.core.encoding.longs
Provides Pebble's core compression implementation specific for lists containing elements of long type.
org.pebble.core.encoding.longs.datastructures
Provides Pebble's core compression utility data structures specific for lists containing elements of long type.
org.pebble.core.exceptions
Provides Pebble's core exceptions.
org.pebble.types
Provides Pebble's encoding and decoding generics types functionality.
org.pebble.types.text
Provides Pebble's encoding and decoding Texts functionality.
org.pebble.types.timestamp
Provides Pebble's encoding and decoding Timestamps functionality.
org.pebble.types.uuid
Provides Pebble's encoding and decoding UUIDs functionality.
org.pebble.utils
Contains utility classes which extends Pebble's core functionality.
